     5→//! Query utilities for Gallops JSON
     6→//!
     7→//! Contains shared utilities used by per-command modules.
     8→//! The original jjrq_run_* command functions have been moved to dedicated modules:
     9→//! - jjrmu_muster.rs (muster)
    10→//! - jjrpd_parade.rs (parade)
    11→//! - jjrsc_scout.rs (scout)
    12→//! - jjrgs_get_spec.rs (get_spec)
    13→//! - jjrgc_get_coronets.rs (get_coronets)
    14→//! - jjrrt_retire.rs (retire)
    15→//! - jjrsd_saddle.rs (saddle)
